  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\"><img alt=\"House Qorgyle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/50px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/75px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/100px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Moriah Qorgyle</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\"><img alt=\"House Qorgyle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/50px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/75px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/100px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Barba_Bolton_Myrielle_Peake_and_Moriah_Qorgyle_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Barba Bolton Myrielle Peake and Moriah Qorgyle by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/Barba_Bolton_Myrielle_Peake_and_Moriah_Qorgyle_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/300px-Barba_Bolton_Myrielle_Peake_and_Moriah_Qorgyle_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/Barba_Bolton_Myrielle_Peake_and_Moriah_Qorgyle_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/450px-Barba_Bolton_Myrielle_Peake_and_Moriah_Qorgyle_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8d/Barba_Bolton_Myrielle_Peake_and_Moriah_Qorgyle_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/600px-Barba_Bolton_Myrielle_Peake_and_Moriah_Qorgyle_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Moriah Qorgyle (right) with Barba Bolton and Myrielle Peake by coldraindropsss</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">House Qorgyle</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Moriah Qorgyle</b> was a noblewoman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">House Qorgyle</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moriah_Qorgyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the death of Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaera_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaera Targaryen\">Jaehaera Targaryen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, Moriah was presented to King Aegon III as a potential bride at the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_Ball\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day Ball\">Maiden's Day Ball</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a>, she had the boldest tongue present, as she requested that the king come down from the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> and kiss her. Aegon did not oblige her request.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moriah_Qorgyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued2)#Moriah_Qorgyle\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued2)\">Moriah Qorgyle</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403190823\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.244 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 669/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10545/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7030/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1588/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1824/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.67 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  234.188      1 -total\n 94.99%  222.455      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 94.43%  221.142      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.38%   24.302     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.73%    8.731      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.10%    7.260      3 Template:Ref\n  2.59%    6.063      2 Template:Date\n  2.11%    4.949      3 Template:Ref/core\n  0.75%    1.759      1 Template:References\n  0.46%    1.086      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in p